## 延伸阅读 Further Reading
　  

<p style="font:bold 150% sans-serif;">儒学前世今生<br />
​​Confucianism - Past and Present</p>

<table style="width:100%;background-color:#efefef;border-collapse:collapse;">
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">1</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　在中国灿烂的文明进程中，儒学思想是极其重要的一条支流，就像长江注入大海那样，几千年来，它也不断地为中华文明注入了血液与活力，并沉淀出了深厚的文化内涵。而有关它的前世今生或可称之为发展历程，则可分为如下几个阶段： 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　In the process of the splendid Chinese civilization , Confucianism is an extremely important tributary of the Yangtze River into the sea like that , thousands of years, it was the Chinese civilization continually injected blood and vitality, and precipitate out of the deep cultural connotation . And about its past lives or can be called development process can be divided into the following phases:

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">2</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

<b>一、儒学起源 </b>

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

<b>A. Confucianism originated</b>

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">3</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　关于儒学的起源，许多学者曾做过考证，但基本说法不一，史无定论。概括起来，约有以下几种论说： 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　On the origin of Confucianism , many scholars have done research, but the basic vary, history inconclusive. To sum up , some of the following discourse :

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">4</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　其一，王官说。“儒家者流，盖出于司徒之官。”（班固：《汉书•艺文志》）由此创立了百家出于王官之说。近人章太炎先生认为：“古之学者，多出王官世卿用事之时，百姓当家，则务农商畜牧，无所谓学问也。其欲学者，不得不给事官府为之胥徒，或乃供洒扫为仆役焉。”（《章太炎政论选集》）简言之，此说主要从王官与儒学有某些相似的职能来立论，它主张古代学术皆出于王官之学，这是由于民间因专事体力劳动而无暇顾及学问，而为了求得学问，则必须服役于官宦才有受书治学的可能。由此，官学成为了诸子之学的渊源，而诸子之学成为了官学延续的结果。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　First, the palace said. " Confucian those streams , the official cover for Stuart 's ." ( Ban : "Han • Art and Literature " ) whereby the creation of hundreds of out palace said. Neighbor Mr Zhang said: "The scholars of ancient , more time王官世Qing Allusion , the people masters , the supplier of livestock farming , it does not matter knowledge but also their desire scholar Xu had to give something official to whom believers , or is to be used as a sweep . Yan servant . " ( " Political Taiyan anthology " ) in short , this theory mainly from the palace and Confucianism have some similar functions to arguments , arguing that are out of the ancient palace of academic science, which is due by specializing in folk physical labor and attend to learning, and in order to seek knowledge , you must have served in the subject may courtiers book scholarship . Thus, the official school of philosophers became the origin of science, and philosophers of science became the official results of the continuation school .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">5</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　其二，世变说。对于“王官说”胡适先生持不同看法：“（王官说）皆属汉儒附会揣测之辞，其言全无凭据”，“诸子之学不但决不能出于王官；果使能与王官并世，亦定不为所容而必为所焚烧坑杀耳。”依据春秋战国时期的动荡背景，胡适提出“学术之兴皆本于世变之所急”，“诸子之学皆春秋战国之时势世变所产生，其一家之兴，无非应时而起。”可见，所谓“世变说”主要专注于儒学起源的历史背景，它认为在一个学说兴起的背后，总有着与之息息相关的时代因素，因此，在春秋战国时诸侯纷争、战乱频发的混乱时局下，儒学起于救世之弊，应时而兴，成为了这个动荡不安的时代的催生物。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Second, the world becomes said. For the " palace said," Mr. Hu Shi took a different view: " ( palace says ) are among the Confucian will be attached to speculation of speech , which made no credentials ," " philosophers of science must not only for palace ; fruit enable the palace and the world would surely not be tolerated and must be burned as abusing the ear . " according to background turbulent Spring and Autumn Period , Hu put forward the" academic interest are the world of the urgency of change " , " the masters of Learn all the times changed the world arising from the Spring and Autumn , the company 's interest , nothing more than seasonal sky . " visible , so-called" change the world , said , " the main focus on the historical background of Confucianism originated , it is considered a doctrine behind the rise in total has factors closely related with the times , therefore, in the Warring States princes disputes chaotic political situation of frequent wars , Confucianism played in the salvation of the disadvantages , should sometimes Xing, became a reminder of this turbulent era creatures.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">6</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　其三，道统说。儒家对于儒学的起源有一套自己的说法，《中庸》中称：“仲尼祖述尧、舜，宪章文、武”；《论语•八佾》从夏、商、周之礼及孔子崇礼的一致性，进一步论述了儒家的道统说。所以，在“道统说”看来，儒家传道的脉络上接尧、舜、文王、武王等贤人，这也意味着它的思想源头可追溯到上古的贤明时期。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Third, Orthodoxy says. For the origins of Confucianism Confucianism have its own statement, "moderate " and said: " ZENY Zushu Yao , Shun, charter Wen, Wu " ; "The Analects • Eight- yi" from the Xia, Shang and Zhou ritual of the ceremony and孔子崇consistency further discusses the Confucian orthodoxy says. So, in " Orthodoxy says ," It seems , then Yao, Shun , King Wen , King Wu et sage Confucius preached on the context , this also means that it 's thinking can be traced back during the ancient sage .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">7</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

<b>二、中国儒学发展的第一个阶段，是以孔子、孟子、荀子等为代表的先秦原始儒学 </b>

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

<b>B. the first phase of the development of Chinese Confucianism , is Confucius, Mencius , Xun Qin as the representative of the original Confucianism</b>

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">8</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　先秦的原始儒学首先是由孔子开创的，其代表人物主要有孟子、荀子等人。从某种角度来讲，原始的儒家学说是为国家、社会培养官吏的学说，是“士”的文化，其特点就是提出了一个理想的社会和与之相对应的理想人格，并规定了许多修身方面的道德规范及从政方面的治国原则。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　The original First Qin Confucianism Confucius pioneered by its representatives are mainly Mencius et al . In some ways in terms of the original Confucian doctrine is for the country , officials of the doctrine of social culture , the culture of "Shi" , which is characterized by raised an ideal society , and corresponding with the ideal personality and provides a lot of ethical and political aspects of governance principles Slim regard.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">9</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　回溯孔子所生活的春秋末期，整个社会发生了一场颠覆性的历史变化，周天子的地位不断下降，而各诸侯则可凭借其势力来提升自己的地位，甚至僭越天子的礼仪。面对这样一个礼崩乐坏、道德沦丧的社会，孔子寄希望于人的本性的自觉，竭力强调“克己”、“修身”和“仁”的学说。所谓“克己”，便是克制、约束自己；“修身”指的是修养身心，努力提高自身的道德修养水平；至于“仁”，孔子将其视为儒家的最高道德规范，认为“己所不欲，勿施于人”为“仁”，“己欲立而立人，己欲达而达人”为“仁”，概括起来，“仁”便是根据自己的内心体验来推测别人的思想感受，以达到推己及人的目的，或者说，“仁”的核心是“爱人”，即在人与人之间构建一种亲善关系，实现与他人的互存、互助、互爱。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Back late Spring and Autumn Confucius lived , there was a whole social history of disruptive change in the status of the Zhou declining , while the princes may by virtue of its power to improve their status, even overstepped the emperor 's ceremonial . The face of such a nature conscious Ceremony Disintegration , morally bankrupt society, Confucius hopes of people , trying to emphasize " self-denial" , "self " and " benevolence" doctrine. The so-called " self-denial" , that is, restraint, discipline themselves ; "self " refers to the cultivation of body and mind, strive to improve their level of morality ; As for the " benevolence" of Confucius it as the highest Confucian ethics , that " what you do not for , do not impose on others " as " benevolence "," Yuli written for the people , he seeks to reach people "as " benevolence " , summed up," benevolence " is, according to their own inner experience feelings of other people's ideas to speculate in order to achieve the purpose of Reciprocity , or that "benevolence" is the core of "love" , that is, between people to build a rapport with others to achieve mutual survival and mutual assistance , mutual love .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">10</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　后世的孟子在继承孔子思想的基础上，以“性善”为根据，推行了“仁政”学说。在他看来，“仁政”适用于思想、政治、经济等各个领域，其基本精神是对人民有深切的同情和爱心。在政治上，孟子认为对一个国家来说“民为贵，社稷次之，君为轻”，百姓是国家之本，统治者若能心存“恻隐之心”并将其推行到实际的统治中，处处考虑民间疾苦，与底层百姓同忧乐，便有望实现“仁政”理想；在经济上，孟子主张“夫仁政，必自经界始。”（《孟子•滕文公上》）有关“仁政”的施行必须要从“经界”开始，要让百姓拥有一定的土地使用权，即所谓的“分田制禄”，“制民恒产”，因为“民之为道也，有恒产者有恒心，无恒产者无恒心”，有产业的百姓会有稳定的心理状态，而无产业的百姓是没有稳定心态的，在这种情况下他们就无所不为，甚至四处犯罪。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Future generations inherit Confucius Mencius on the basis of the " goodness " as the basis for the implementation of the " benevolent " doctrine. In his opinion, " benevolent " applies to all areas of ideological, political , economic , etc., the basic spirit of the people have deep sympathy and love. Politically, Mencius believed that for a nation , " people are the boat followed the king of light" , the people of this country is , if the rulers feel " compassion " and the actual implementation of the rule , the sufferings of the people everywhere to consider , with the people concerned with the underlying music, it is expected to achieve " benevolent " ideal ; . " benevolent husband , will start from the business circles " in the economy , Mencius advocated ( "Mencius • Tengwen Gong on " ) on " benevolent " purposes must be seen " by the world " began to let people have a certain amount of land use rights , the so-called " sub- field system Lu "," people constant production system , "because " people are way too , Possessions perseverance , without constant production had no perseverance , " there are industry people have stable psychological state , and no industry is no stable state of mind of the people , in this case they will stop at nothing , even around crime .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">11</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　与孔、孟相比，荀子的思想虽然保留了理想主义的成分，但与此同时，它也显现出一种现实主义倾向。他在重视礼义道德教育的同时，也强调了政法制度的惩罚作用。他认为人的本性并不美好，顺着人性的自然发展必然造成社会的争乱。因此，必须用礼义、法度等去引导、改造人的自然本性，即所谓的“化性起伪”，然后才能使之合乎群体社会的公共原则与要求。所以，荀子在强调自我修养、道德自觉之重要性的同时，更为强调“师”与“法”的教育与规范作用。例如他说：“礼者，所以正身也；师者，所以正礼也。无礼何以正身，无师吾安知礼之为是也。”（《荀子•修身》）又如：“从人之性，顺人之情，必出于争夺，合于犯分乱理，而归于暴。故必将有师法之化，礼义之道，然后出于辞让，合于文理，而归于治。”（《荀子•性恶》）同样，荀子设计的治国原则也有着较为鲜明的现实主义特征，如“明分使群”、“群居和一之道”等，它们基本都是在肯定当时已形成的社会等级和职业分工的基础上，来规定社会每一位成员的名分、位置，并要求其各尽其职，从而达到整个社会的和谐一致。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Compared with Confucius, Mencius , Xun Zi 's thought , while retaining the idealism of ingredients, but at the same time , it also showed a tendency to realism . His emphasis on propriety and moral education , but also emphasizes the role of political and legal system of punishment . He believes that human nature is not good , along the natural development of human society will inevitably lead to contention chaos. Therefore, we must use to guide propriety , testimonies , etc., transform human nature , so-called " resistance from pseudo " before making it public in line with the principles and requirements of groups in society . So, in emphasizing the importance of self-cultivation Zi , moral consciousness of the same time, more emphasis on " teacher" and "law" of education and normative role . For example, he said: . " Eli , so there is also seating arrangement ; division , so there are also rude why ceremony seating arrangement , without a teacher I know that the ceremony was a too " ( "Zi • Slim" ) Another example : "From the people of resistance, along touched the will out compete , qualifying guilty of disorderly management, and attributed to the storm . thus bound to have imitated the technology , propriety of the road , then out politely refuse , qualifying for Arts , and attributed to governance. " ( " Zi • Evil " ) Similarly, the principle of the rule of Zi also has a more distinctive design features of realism , such as" make out of the group , "" gregarious Road "one of , etc., which are basically in the affirmative then the basis of social class and professional division formed on to the provisions birthright of every member of society , location, and request to play his part to achieve the harmony of the whole society .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">12</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　原始儒家在先秦春秋末至战国时期，是社会上具有广泛影响的“显学”之一。他们提倡的道德修养学说在“士”阶层中有着深远的影响，而他们所设计的理想政治制度和治国原则，则因饱含理想主义成分，不如法家思想那样契合当时诸侯称霸、群雄割据的社会现实，因而始终没有能得到当权者的赏识、采用。所以，原始儒家学说与后来成为实际社会制度依据的儒学不同，它还只是一种关于道德修养和政治理想的一般性学说。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　秦春秋prior to the end of the original Confucian Warring States period, is one of the " significant learning" has a broad impact on society. They advocate the doctrine of morality has in the " disabilities" hierarchy profound impact , but the ideal political system and governance principles they design , full of idealism due to ingredients that fit was not as good as Legalism princes dominate , separatist warlords social reality , and thus never get appreciated by those in power , using . Therefore, the original Confucianism and later became a social system based on different actual Confucianism , it is just a general theory about morality and political ideals .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">13</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

<b>三、中国儒学发展的第二个阶段，是以董仲舒、《白虎通义》为代表的两汉政治制度化和宗教化的儒学 </b>

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

<b>C. the second phase of the development of Chinese Confucianism , is Zhongshu , " White tiger justice" as the representative of Han political institutionalization of Confucianism and religion</b>

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">14</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　两汉时期可以视为儒学发展的第二个阶段。在这个阶段中，儒学不仅在理论方面吸收了先秦时期其他一些学派的思想（特别是阴阳五行学家的思想），内容上获得了极为丰厚的充实，而且还被确立为官方的主流思想，为统治阶级所用，成为了政治统治的御用之学。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Han Dynasty Confucianism can be considered as the second phase of development . At this stage, not only in the theory of Confucianism during the Qin Dynasty absorbed some of the other school of thought (especially the idea of yin and yang scientist ) , to obtain a very lucrative enrich the content, but also established as the official mainstream thinking , as used by the ruling class , has become a political rule of the Queen of the school .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">15</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　相对于先秦的原始儒学，汉代儒学最明显的一个变化，就是被两汉的儒者们予以宗教化、政治化和制度化。这里不得不提及西汉时期的大儒董仲舒，他的学说不仅接受和发扬了荀子关于礼法并重、刑德兼用的理论，而且还大量吸收了墨家“兼爱”、“尚同”的理论，乃至墨家学说中某些带有宗教色彩的思想。而更为突出的是，在他专攻的春秋公羊学中，充满了阴阳家的阴阳五行学说，并使阴阳五行思想成为汉以后儒家学说中的一个重要组成部分。班固在《汉书•五行志》中说：“董仲舒治公羊春秋，始推阴阳，为儒者宗”，就清楚地指出了这一事实。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Relative to the original Confucianism Qin , the Han Confucianism most obvious change is to be Han Confucian religion have been politicized and institutionalized. Theory here have mentioned the Western Han Dynasty Confucian scholars Zhongshu , his doctrine is not only accepted and carried forward Zi etiquette both on theoretical punishment Germany combined , but also absorbs the Mohist "universal love ", " still the same " , and even Mohists Some doctrine with religious ideas . The more prominent is that in his school specializing in the Spring and Autumn Annals , full of Naturalists theory of yin and yang , yin and yang make after Han Confucian ideology became an important part. Ban on "Han • Five records," said: " Dong Zhongshu rule Rams Spring , began to push the yin and yang , as Confucians cases ", it clearly points out this fact.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">16</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　董仲舒对于儒学的发展不仅在于学理方面，而更在于他把儒学推向政治制度化和宗教化的方向。在有关儒学政治化的过程中，他推行“罢黜百家，独尊儒术”，尊称孔子为“素王”，并将《春秋》说成是孔子为汉朝预先制定好的一部制度建设和国家治理的纲领。这样，儒学就开始与当时实际的社会政治制度联系了起来。不过，这在董仲舒时代仅仅是一个开始，直至东汉章帝时，由皇帝亲自主持召集大儒们举行了一次“白虎观”会议，会后由著名学者班固整理纂集出《白虎通德论》，这才真正完成了把儒家一部分主要学说转变为实际的社会政治制度的律条以及社会全体成员共同必须遵循的道德规范。从此以后，儒学已不再是单纯的伦理道德修养和政治理想的学说，而是同时具有了一种社会制度方面的律条的作用。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Dong Zhongshu lies not only in the development of Confucianism and theoretical aspects , but also because he Confucianism and religion into political institutionalization of direction. In the course of about Confucianism politicized , he launched " deposed hundreds , Only Confucianism " Confucius revered as " prime king " and "Spring" Han said to Confucius as a pre-established institution building and national program of governance. Thus , Confucianism began with the then actual social and political systems link up. However, this is only a start in Zhongshu times, until when Han Zhang Di , held a "White Tiger Concept ' meeting convened by the emperor personally presided over the Confucian scholars who , after finishing compile by the famous scholar Ban set out the " White tiger Strickland , "which really work together to complete the Confucian doctrine into practical part of the main social and political systems of law and all members of society must follow the code of ethics . Since then, Confucianism is no longer a mere political ideals of morality and ethical doctrine , but also has the effect of law of a social system.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">17</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　与此同时，两汉时期也出现了一股把儒学宗教化的倾向。围绕着五经，那个时代的儒者们撰写了很多著作，这些著作因辅佐经书而被称为“纬书”。董仲舒和当时所流传的纬书都不断地把“天”描绘成儒学中至高无上的神，如董仲舒说 “天者，百神之大君也”（《春秋繁露•郊祭》），并且竭力宣扬天是有意志的，能与人相感应的，而王者是“承天意以从事”的等等一整套宗教神学理论。孔子是儒学的创始人，自然也就成了教王。在当时流传的大量纬书中，不仅把孔子说成是神的儿子，而且把他的相貌也描绘成与一般凡人极不相同的怪模样。可见从两汉儒学发展的历史来看，儒学的宗教化是与儒学的政治制度化密切相关且同步进行的，前者是为使后者得以成立和巩固服务的。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Meanwhile, the Han Dynasty also emerged in the Confucian religious tendency . Around the Pentateuch, that era Confucian who has written many books, these books were written by his assistant, was called " weishu ." Dong Zhongshu and then floated weishu are constantly put "day" portrayed as the supreme god of Confucianism , such as Dong Zhongshu said, " those days , Maharaja hundred God also " ( " Chun Qiu Fan Lu • Country Festival" ) , and has endeavored to promote there will be a day , with one -phase induction , while the king is "commitment to engage in an act of God ," and so a set of religious theology . Confucius was the founder of Confucianism , naturally became Pope . At that time a lot of latitude in the book spread , not only Confucius said to be the son of God , and his general appearance also portrayed as very different mortal strange appearance . Seen from a historical point of view the development of the Han Confucianism , Confucianism is a religion of Confucianism is closely related to political institutionalization , and simultaneously , the former for the latter to be the establishment and consolidation of services.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">18</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　到了汉末，政治制度化了的儒学礼教（名教），一方面成为束缚和压制人的自然感情的东西，一方面又成了那些伪君子沽名钓誉的工具，因而引起了人们的强烈不满。玄学乘此流弊而起，调和名教与自然（性情）的矛盾，而其中又都强调以“自然”为本。并且在理论学说上，玄学也明确地提出了“道明其本，儒言其用”（《后汉书》卷十二“袁宏曰”）。所以，自从玄学诞生以后，儒学尽管在政治制度层面仍然保持着它的统治地位，而在思想修养层面的功能，却已为玄学或道家（以及道教）所取代。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　To the late Han Dynasty , Confucian ethics of political institutionalization ( Norm ) , on the one hand and the suppression of human bondage became emotional nature of things , one of those tools became hypocrites fame , and thus aroused strong dissatisfaction. Metaphysics take this abuse sky, Norm and reconcile contradictory nature ( nature ) , of which they stressed the " nature" oriented. And the doctrine , metaphysics also made it clear that the " Dominic the book, Confucianism made its use" ( "Han" Volume Twelve " Yuan Hong said " ) . So, since the birth of metaphysics , Confucian political system level despite still maintained its dominance , but in ideological training level functions , they are replaced by metaphysics or Taoism ( and Taoism ) .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">19</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

<b>四、中国儒学发展的第三个阶段，是以程、朱、陆、王等为代表的宋、明、清时期的性理之学（即理学）的儒学 </b>

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

<b>D. the third stage of the development of Chinese Confucianism , based on Cheng Zhu , Lu and Wang as the representative of the Song, Ming and Qing Dynasties grounds on the school ( ie Science ) Confucianism</b>

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">20</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　在魏、晋、南北朝时期，甚至一直到唐代，由于玄学和佛教的冲击，儒学在人们的思想领域和一般人的精神生活里，已经不占据一个主导地位了（但它在政治制度方面的地位仍是主导性的）。但至宋明时期，儒学却在某种程度上恢复了作为伦理道德、身心修养层面的社会功能，从而与作为政治制度层面的儒学相呼应配合，进一步强化了它在社会政教两方面的效用。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　In the Wei , Jin, Northern and Southern Dynasties , even until the Tang Dynasty, due to the impact of metaphysics and Buddhism , Confucianism in the field of people's minds and people's spiritual life in general , does not occupy a dominant position (but it 's position in the political system still the dominant ) . But to the Song and Ming Dynasties , Confucianism , but in a way as to restore the moral , physical and mental training level social function, and thus the level of Confucianism as a political system with echoes , and further strengthen its effectiveness in terms of both political and religious society .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">21</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　这一时期的儒者们借鉴佛道心性形上学理论，主动深入到儒学内部，发掘可与佛道相抗衡的理论与经典根据，并据此建立起了儒学的心性修养的形上学理论体系。《易》和《中庸》正是宋明性理学家发挥儒学性命形而上原理，并用以与佛、道抗衡的主要经典依据。被推誉为理学开创者的北宋五子（即周敦颐、张载、邵雍、程颢、程颐），无一例外地都是借阐发《易》理来建立他们的理论体系。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　We learn from this period Confucian theory of Buddhist metaphysics Mind , active deep into the interior of Confucianism , Buddhism and Taoism excavations can compete with the classical theory based on , and accordingly established a theoretical system of Confucian metaphysics Mind accomplishment . "Easy " and " Mean" is Neo- Confucianism lives of physicists play a metaphysical principle , and for the Buddhist and Taoist classics compete primarily based . Science hailed as pioneers pushed Northern Song Wuzi ( ie Zhou , Zhang Zai , Shao Yong , Cheng Hao , Cheng Yi ) , without exception, are expounded by the "easy " reason to build their theories.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">22</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　性理学（即理学）以继承尧、舜、禹、汤、文、武、周公、孔、孟的道统和复兴儒学为己任。不过，它欲复兴的儒学，主要不是政治制度层面的儒学，而是伦理道德、身心修养层面的儒学，以便重新充分发挥出儒学在道德修养方面的社会功能，夺回被佛、道占据了七百年优势的身心修养、思想理论领域。再则，理学所复兴的儒学，无论是在内容上还是在形式上，也都与先秦原始儒学有了很大的不同。原始儒学旨在阐发一些具体的伦理道德规范、治国安邦的实践原则，而对于这些原则的根据何在等形而上的理论问题则很少探讨，然而理学却在阐发原始儒学的基本实践原则时，竭力从形上学理论方面给予提高。例如，程颐在论“仁”时曾说：“医家以不认痛痒谓之不仁，人以不知觉不认义理为不仁，譬最近。”（《二程集》，《河南程氏遗书》卷第二上）就已把“仁”提升到了“义理”的高度，即提高到行为规范的“所以然”来认识。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Of Science ( ie Science ) to inherit Yao, Shun , Yu, Tang , Wen, Wu , the Duke of Zhou , Confucius, Mencius 's revival of Confucian orthodoxy and responsibility . However, it is the revival of Confucianism want , not primarily Confucian political system level , but moral , physical and mental training aspects of Confucianism , give full play to re- Confucian social function in terms of morality , recapture Buddhism, Taoism occupy seven hundred On the advantages of physical and mental training , ideological and theoretical fields. Furthermore , the revival of Confucianism Confucianism , either in form or in content , have also made a big difference with the original Qin Confucianism . Original Confucianism aims to elucidate some specific code of ethics , practice the principle of country and bringing peace , and for these principles are rarely discussed what the theoretical issues such as metaphysical , but elucidation of basic pharmacology , but in practice when the original principles of Confucianism , trying giving increased from metaphysical theory . For example , Cheng Yi in theory " benevolence" when he said : . " Physicians to recognize their primary concern is not that of heartless people do not recognize the moral principles of not perceived as heartless analogy recently " ( "two -way set" , "Henan Cheng suicide note ." volume II on ) had the "benevolence" elevated to the " moral principles " in height , up to a code of conduct that is " why " to understand .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">23</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　宋明清性理之学对儒学的重大发展，是与它积极吸收和融合玄学、佛教、道教（和道家）的理论为己所用分不开的。理学强调“天理当然”、“自然合理”等，这与玄学的“物无妄然必由其理”（王弼《周易略例•明彖》）、“依乎天理”（郭象《庄子•人间世》注）、“天理自然”（同前《齐物论》注）等思想联系密切。而理学核心理论中的“理一分殊”、“体用一源”等，也吸收于佛教，其中尤其是与佛教华严学中的“法界缘起”，以及“六相圆融”、“理事无碍”等理论的启发有关。佛教讲“一月普现一切水，一切水月一月摄”，天上的月亮映在地上的千万条江河里面，它都是一个完整的反映，所以佛教认为“理”是一个整体，而“事”是“理”的各种各样的特殊反映，“理”和“事”是无碍的，所谓“无碍”就是圆融的。进一步讲，因为每件事里面都有一个相同的理，那么事与事之间其实也就是无碍的，这就叫“事事无碍”。通过这些基本理论的发展，性理学大大地丰富了儒学的知识论和修养论理论，也由此建立起了儒家的形而上学体系。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Song Ming and Qing grounds on major developments in the science of Confucianism , with its positive absorption and integration of metaphysics , Buddhism , Taoism ( and Taoism ) theory for its own use inseparable. Science stressed that " justice course ", " natural and reasonable " and so on , which is metaphysics " No matter rashly will by reason" ( Wang Bi "Book slightly case • Ming hog " ) , "according to almost heaven " ( Guo Xiang "Zhuangzi • Room World " note ) , " natural justice " (op. cit " Equality of Things " note ) and other ideas closely linked . The pharmacology core theory of "Reason Fenshu " , "body with a source ," and so on , but also absorbed in Buddhism, which especially Avatamsaka Buddhist school in the " Dharma origin " and " six-phase harmony ", " governing without inspired by the theory of obstacle , " and so on. Buddhism stresses " Jan & P is now all water, all elusive January intake ," the moon reflected on the ground ten million rivers inside, it is a complete reflection of Buddhism so that " truth" is a whole, and " it " is the "truth" of a variety of special reflection , "truth" and " thing" is harmless , so-called " harmless " is the harmony of . Further, because everything which has an identical rationale , then between what is and what is actually harmless , which is called " Shishiwuai ." By developing these basic theory of jurisprudence greatly enriched the theory of knowledge and accomplishment Theory of Confucianism , has thus established a Confucian metaphysical system.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">24</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　宋明以后，儒学这种两个层面、两种社会功能的一致化，使得许多本来属于伦理修养层面的问题与政治制度层面的问题纠缠在一起而分割不清。而且由于伦理修养层面是直接为政治制度层面服务的，常常使得原本建立在自觉原则上的规范变而为强制人们接受的律条。而这种以“天理”、“良心”来规范的律条，有时比明文规定的律条更为严厉。“人死于法，犹有怜之者；死于理，其谁怜之。”（《孟子字义疏证》卷上）这是对性理学所引生出的社会流弊的深刻反映。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　After Neo Confucianism which two levels, consistent with the social functions of the two , so many have been part of the ethical aspects of the problem of self-cultivation and political system -level issues intertwined and segmentation unclear. And because ethics training level is the level of service directly to the political system , often making conscious originally built on the principles and norms change the law to force people to accept article . And this kind of " justice ", " conscience" to the norms of law , sometimes more than express provision of the law is more stringent . "People die of law , worse than pity those ; died management, its who pity ." ( " Mencius Hermeneutics card" on the volume ) which is the birth of jurisprudence cited reflect profound social evils .

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">25</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

<b>五、中国儒学发展的新阶段，是从康有为开始的，与西方近代民主、科学思想交流融通的近现代新儒学 </b>

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

<b>E. a new stage of development of Chinese Confucianism , Kang Youwei from the beginning, with the Western democratic ideas of modern science and modern facility near New Confucianism</b>

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">26</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　十九世纪中叶以后，随着中国封建制度的开始解体，当时以性理学为代表的儒学也走向了衰落。此时，在外国资本主义的武力、经济、政治、文化的侵略和渗透下，中国面临着亡国灭种的危急局面。而此时的儒学，不管在制度层面还是在思想意识层面，都在相当程度上起着阻碍社会改革和进步的作用。在西方经济、政治、文化的冲击下，儒学遭到了激烈的批判，从而到了不进行变革就无法继续生存下去的局面。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　After the mid-nineteenth century , with the beginning of the disintegration of China 's feudal system was represented sexual Neo Confucianism also to the decline . At this point , in the force of foreign capitalism , economic, political, cultural aggression and penetration, China is facing a critical situation subjugation and genocide . At a time of Confucianism , regardless of ideology or in the level, at the institutional level plays a considerable extent hinder the role of social reform and progress . Under the impact of Western economic, political , cultural, Confucianism was a fierce critique , so to change without unable to survive the situation.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">27</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　中国儒学的向近代转化，或者说把传统儒家思想与近代西方文化连结、融通起来，有一说以为是从康有为开始的。他虽然打着托古改制的旗帜，在宣传维新变法思想时，总要引经据典地到中国传统儒家学说中去寻找合适的言论，以证明他所推行的社会改革方案也正是古代圣贤们孜孜以求的理想，但在另一方面，他同时也对儒家孔、孟学说做了许多新的解释和发挥，使其符合于当时人们所了解的西方文化，并以此证明他所推崇的传统儒学是完全合乎时代潮流的。但是，康有为为儒学现代转化的探索并不成功。其中一个主要原因是，他还是要把政治制度层面的儒学与思想修养层面的儒学捆在一起。他不仅根本没有想过要把这两个不同层面的儒学区分开来，甚至主张把儒学改造成为宗教，并在宪法上把孔教规定为国教。这些主张在当时的历史条件下，是很难为正在为推翻封建专制统治而奋斗的人们所接受的。 

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　Chinese Confucianism to the modern transformation of traditional Confucianism or link with modern Western culture, factoring up , there is a saying that from the beginning of Kang Youwei . Although he asked the name of the ancient banner of reform , political reform in the宣传维new ideas , always quote the classics to the Chinese traditional Confucianism to find the right words to prove his social reform programs implemented by the ancient sages is also pursued the ideal but on the other hand , he also Confucian Confucius, Mencius doctrine did a lot of new interpretations and play to match the time people know about Western culture , and to prove that he respected traditional Confucianism is entirely consistent with the times trends. However , Kang was to explore the modern transformation of Confucianism was not successful . One of the main reasons is that he put the political system -level aspects of Confucianism and Confucian ideology accomplishment tied together . He not only did not want to think about these two different levels of Confucianism to distinguish , even advocated the Confucianism transformed into religious and constitutional provisions to Confucianism as the state religion . These claims under the historical conditions , it is difficult for the overthrow of the feudal autocratic rule is the struggle of people to accept.

</td></tr>
<tr><td style="width:2%;background-color:#fff;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.7em">28</td>
<td style="width:38%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:1em">

　　二十世纪二十年代以后，由于清皇朝已被推翻，封建专制政治制度从名义上已不再存在。因此，除了小部分当权者继续企图把儒学与社会政治制度联系在一起外，更多的人则是把儒学作为传统思想文化遗产，做学理方面的研究。这些人所关心的是，在西方文化冲击下如何汇通儒学与西方文化，如何继承和发扬儒学的优秀传统，以保持民族的自主精神等问题。这时涌现出了一批关心儒学命运和前途的学者，如梁漱溟、熊十力、马一浮、钱穆、冯友兰、贺麟等，他们都在汇通中西方文化的前提下，来解释儒学、发展儒学，乃至建立起某种新的儒学体系。而他们的共同愿望，也可以说都包含通过对儒学的现代阐释，发扬民族传统文化，使其在当代人的思想道德修养和民族主体意识的确立方面发挥积极的作用。

</td><td style="width:1%;background-color:#fff"></td><td style="width:49%;padding:2px 10px;vertical-align:top;font-size:0.85em">

　　After the 1920s , the Qing Dynasty was overthrown , the feudal autocratic political system nominally no longer exists. Therefore , in addition to a small part of the authorities to continue to attempt to Confucianism and social and political systems together , the more people are thinking of the Confucian heritage as a traditional , theoretical aspects of doing research . These people care about is how Huitong Confucianism and Western culture , and how to inherit and carry forward the fine traditions of Confucianism under the impact of Western culture in order to maintain the spirit of national self and other issues. Then emerged a number of concerns the fate and future of Confucian scholars, such as Liang Shuming , Xiong , Ma Yifu , Qian , Feng , He Lin , etc., under the premise that they are in the Land of Western culture , to explain Confucianism , the development of Confucianism , and even build from some new Confucian system. And their common aspiration , it can be said is contained by a modern interpretation of Confucianism , carry forward traditional national culture , to play an active role in the establishment of contemporary ideological and moral cultivation and the nation 's consciousness .

</td></tr>
</table>
　  

